Abstract = {Organic phototransistors have attracted tremendous attentions due to
   their light weight and good compatibility with flexible substrates.
   However, developing organic phototransistors with high performance over
   the broadband spectrum still remains great challenge. In this study,
   high-performance broadband phototransistor is developed with organic
   materials/MXene, which exhibits improved mobility and outstanding
   photodetection characteristics. The combination of MXene and organic
   semiconductor materials provides a promising way to prepare
   high-performance OPT with broadband detection.},
